description: Bacon Bacon is taking the best that tender pork has to offer and serving it all up to major bacon fans all throughout San Francisco. Come out to this truck and treat yourself to a savory feast of Double Bacon Cheeseburgers, the L.G.B.T. (gee, it’s that goat cheese that makes this creation a foodie favorite), big ole Breakfast Burritos and Sandwiches, Bacon Grilled Cheese, Banh Mi, and much more, all with tasty crispy bacon piled high. Is all this makin’ you hungry? Well Bacon Bacon has the cure for you.
name: Bacon Bacon
